                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100718-45-off264 t18100718-45-cd265"></join>, about the hour of two at night, being in the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18100718-45-victim479" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Snow
